WEBVTT

00:00:28.147 --> 00:00:31.507
Biz rivojlanib, hasharotlar bizning
parhez an'analarimizga aylanganida,

00:00:31.531 --> 00:00:35.368
ular asosiy oziq-ovqat va
noziklikning rolini bajardilar.

00:00:35.392 --> 00:00:39.250
Qadimgi Yunonistonda sikadalarga 
hashamatli taom sifatida qaralgan.

00:00:39.274 --> 00:00:43.016
Va hatto Rimliklar ham qo'ng'iz 
lichinkalarini g'ayrioddiy deb topganlar.

00:00:43.040 --> 00:00:45.125
Nega biz qumursqalarga
bo'lgan ehtiyojimizni

00:00:45.149 --> 00:00:47.971
yo'qotdik? Bunday 
cheklanishimizning sababi tarixga borib

00:00:47.995 --> 00:00:49.541
taqaladi va bu voqea, ehtimol

00:00:49.565 --> 00:00:52.773
miloddan avvalgi 10000 - yilda 
O'rta Sharqda

00:00:52.797 --> 00:00:54.248
qishloq xo'jaligining asosiy

00:00:54.272 --> 00:00:56.757
vatani bo'lgan 
Fertil Crescent da boshlanadi.

00:00:56.781 --> 00:01:01.333
O'sha vaqtlarda ko'chmanchi bo'lgan ajdod-
larimiz Crescent ga joylasha boshlashdi.